content": "想改变世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814542}, {"id": 241169, "content": "只因领导一句话女孩子也要学点东西，然后就从文职转向做造价。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096970}, {"id": 241170, "content": "团队，还有待遇，还有钱吧。", "image": "img/option/option/20171011174854FjHqbQZl17X2DRyJ.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736147}, {"id": 241171, "content": "就那天那天那天那天那天那天那个你那天你今天能调节调节体内调节体内天兵天将太好听好听好听几天呢人今天就能调节调节调节体内途牛太好听不好听不表态吧拜托你那天那天不能停", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143756}, {"id": 241173, "content": "每次遇到傻b老板的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960893}, {"id": 242197, "content": "你们把我想说的了，我该说啥好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157551}, {"id": 241174, "content": "人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622007}, {"id": 241175, "content": "不交五险一金的单位", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910745}, {"id": 241176, "content": "钱少 离家远 公司事儿多", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749624}, {"id": 241177, "content": "站在一个商人的角度向钱看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 241178, "content": "环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883845}, {"id": 241179, "content": "假期，通勤距离，同事，老板", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450673}, {"id": 241180, "content": "没有漂亮的男/女同事 共事，没有动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781661}, {"id": 241181, "content": "钱少事少，感觉在虚度光阴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069025}, {"id": 241182, "content": "混吃等死的同事 低效的工作状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914820}, {"id": 241183, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count